"col-md-5 latestImage"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/faith/2020/06/09/irish-americans-protests-black-lives-matter-george-floyd-history" hreflang="en"><img src="https://www.americamagazine.org/sites/default/files/styles/latest_from_america/public/main_image/AP20166107422272.jpg?itok=XTuYnAlb" width="459" height="305" alt="" typeof="Image" class="img-responsive" /></a></div><div class="col-md-5 latestListingContent"><div class="latestTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/faith/2020/06/09/irish-americans-protests-black-lives-matter-george-floyd-history" hreflang="en">Irish-Americans tempted to condemn today’s protests should remember their history</a></div><div class="latestContent">Black men strung up and lynched by Irish-Americans in New York, in the midst of the Civil War. It turns the stomach to acknowledge, but the truth is unavoidable.</div><div class="authorTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/voices/edward-hoyt" hreflang="en">Edward Hoyt</a><span>June 15, 2020</span></div></div></div></div><div><div class="row latestListing"><div class="col-md-5 latestImage"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/arts-culture/2020/06/15/marriage" hreflang="en"><img src="https://www.americamagazine.org/sites/default/files/styles/latest_from_america/public/main_image/debby-hudson-joKme0a_XV8-unsplash.jpg?itok=wdIf9jvn" width="459" height="305" alt="" typeof="Image" class="img-responsive" /></a></div><div class="col-md-5 latestListingContent"><div class="latestTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/arts-culture/2020/06/15/marriage" hreflang="en">Marriage </a></div><div class="latestContent">while around us the rude populations were moaning</div><div class="authorTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/voices/dan-obrien-0" hreflang="und">Dan O&#039;Brien</a><span>June 15, 2020</span></div></div></div></div><div><div class="row latestListing"><div class="col-md-5 latestImage"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/politics-society/2020/06/15/supreme-court-says-federal-law-protects-lgbt-workers-discrimination" hreflang="en"><img src="https://www.americamagazine.org/sites/default/files/styles/latest_from_america/public/main_image/20200615T1319-351-CNS-SCOTUS-LGBT-EMPLOYEES_800.jpg?itok=QwnjujfJ" width="459" height="305" alt="" typeof="Image" class="img-responsive" /></a></div><div class="col-md-5 latestListingContent"><div class="latestTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/politics-society/2020/06/15/supreme-court-says-federal-law-protects-lgbt-workers-discrimination" hreflang="en">Supreme Court says federal law protects L.G.B.T. workers from discrimination</a></div><div class="latestContent">The decision was for two consolidated cases about fired gay employees and a separate case concerning a fired transgender worker who had sued for employment discrimination after being fired.</div><div class="authorTitle"><a href="https://www.americamagazine.org/voices/ap-cns-rns-staff-and-other-sources" hreflang="und">From AP, CNS, RNS, Staff and other sources</a><span>June 15, 2020</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="block-dfptagarticleleaderboardbtf728x90970x90" class="all-page-articles-leaderboard-btf block block-dfp block-dfp-adb57ade60-602f-430b-a973-80109a429464 clearfix"><div id="js-dfp-tag-article_leaderboard_btf_728x90_970x90"><script type="text/javascript">
